			<id-00013>
				<level type="number">1</level>
				<name type="string">Diligent Student</name>
				<text type="formattedtext">
					<p>At 1st level, a scroll scholar chooses one Knowledge skill. This becomes a class skill if it is not already one. The scroll scholar adds half her class level to all Knowledge checks of this type (minimum 1). At 5th level and every five levels thereafter, a scroll scholar chooses 1 additional Knowledge skill to receive this bonus. For clerics, this ability replaces one of the 1st-level granted powers from her domains&#151;the character gets to choose which of her two 1st-level granted powers it replaces. For wizards, this ability replaces diviner&#146;s fortune (if a diviner) or hand of the apprentice (if a universalist).</p>
