			<id-00007>
				<level type="number">1</level>
				<name type="string">Hidden Bond</name>
				<text type="formattedtext">
					<p>A bonded wizard can change the appearance and magical aura of her bonded item at will, as if using disguise self and magic aura, but affecting only the item; for the purpose of disguise self, the item&#146;s item type (such as weapon or ring) is its creature type.</p>
